that's why we have the append

00:27:55.096 --> 00:27:55.356 A:middle
APIs.

00:27:55.356 --> 00:27:57.066 A:middle
You can append items and

00:27:57.066 --> 00:27:57.586 A:middle
sections.

00:27:58.836 --> 00:28:00.316 A:middle
Now, in that familiar path,

00:27:58.836 --> 00:28:00.316 A:middle
Now, in that familiar path,

00:28:00.316 --> 00:28:01.106 A:middle
where you have a number of

