pretty.

00:28:19.066 --> 00:28:19.956 A:middle
All right, so let's talk a bit

00:28:19.956 --> 00:28:21.246 A:middle
about identifiers.

00:28:21.986 --> 00:28:22.896 A:middle
These have to be unique.

00:28:23.386 --> 00:28:25.726 A:middle
